  <Name>Abi-Dalzim's Horrid Wilting</Name>
  <CastingTime>1 action</CastingTime>
  <Range>150 feet</Range>
  <Duration>Instantaneous</Duration>
  <Level>8</Level>
  <Description>You draw the moisture from every creature in a 30-foot cube centered on a point you choose within range. Each creature in that area must make a Constitution saving throw. Constructs and undead aren't affected, and plants and water elementals make this saving throw with disadvantage. A creature takes 10d8 necrotic damage on a failed save, or half as much damage on a successful one.</Description>
